<body id="page-top">

  <!-- Page Wrapper -->
  <div id="wrapper">

    <!-- Sidebar -->
    <% include partials/nav.ejs %>
    <!-- End of Sidebar -->

    <!-- Content Wrapper -->
    <div id="content-wrapper" class="d-flex flex-column">

      <!-- Main Content -->
      <div id="content">

        <!-- Topbar -->
        <% include partials/top-nav.ejs %>

        <!-- End of Topbar -->

        <!-- Begin Page Content -->
        <div class="container-fluid">

          <!-- Page Heading -->
          <div class="d-sm-flex align-items-center justify-content-between mb-4">
            <h4 class="m-0 font-weight-bold text-primary">------10.11 - Partner Independence Declaration------</h4>            
          </div>          


          <form action="/planning/partner-independence-declaration/:user" method="POST">
            <!-- Content Row -->
          <div class="row">

            <!-- Content Column -->
            <div class="col-lg-12 mb-4">

              <!-- Engagement details Card -->
              
                <% include partials/engagementCard.ejs %>

              <!-- Additional Engagement Card-->                
              <div class="card shadow mb-4">
                <div class="card-header py-3">
                  <h6 class="m-0 font-weight-bold text-primary">Engagement Details</h6>
                </div>
                <div class="card-body">
                    
                    <label class="small font-weight-bold" for="engagementPartner">Engagement Partner
                        <input class="form-control form-control-sm" type="text" id="engagementPartner" name="engagementPartner">
                    </label>                   
                    <label class="small font-weight-bold" for="meetingDate">Date
                        <input class="form-control form-control-sm" type="date" id="today" name="today" readonly>
                    </label><br>
                    <label class="small font-weight-bold">Team Members</label><br>
                    <label class="small font-weight-bold" for="eqcr">EQCR
                        <input class="form-control form-control-sm" type="text" id="eqcr" name="eqcr">
                    </label>
                    <label class="small font-weight-bold" for="manager">Manager
                        <input class="form-control form-control-sm" type="text" id="manager" name="manager">
                    </label>
                    <label class="small font-weight-bold" for="senior">Senior
                        <input class="form-control form-control-sm" type="text" id="senior" name="senior">
                    </label><br>
                    <label class="small font-weight-bold" for="assistants">Assistants
                        <textarea class="form-control form-control-sm" id="assistants" name="assistants" cols="24" rows="6"></textarea>
                    </label>
                </div>
              </div>           


              <!--Independence Declaration Card-->
              <div class="card shadow mb-4">

                <!-- Card Header - Accordion -->
                <a href="#independenceDeclarationCard" class="d-block card-header py-3" data-toggle="collapse" role="button" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapseCardExample">
                    <h6 class="m-0 font-weight-bold text-primary">INDEPENDENCE DECLARATION<br>ENGAGEMENT PARTNER</h6>
                </a>

                <!-- Card Content - Collapse -->
                <div class="collapse" id="independenceDeclarationCard">

                  <div class="card-body">                 

                    I hereby confirm that all the members of the engagement team comply with the firms ethical and independence requirements. 
                    <br><br>

                    I hereby confirm that all the members of the engagement team comply with the IFAC  Code and they are not aware of any transgressions thereof. 
                    <br><br>

                    I have communicated ethical and independence requirements to personnel.  I have remained alert for evidence of non-compliance with ethical and independence requirements by observation and inquiry where applicable. 
                    <br><br>

                    Where matters have come to my attention that indicate that members of the engagement team have not complied with these requirements, I, in consultation with the Managing Board of Partners, will determine appropriate action.
                    <br><br>

                    I have obtained relevant information from the firm and network firms to identify and evaluate circumstances and relationships that create threats to independence.
                    <br><br>

                    I have evaluated information on identified breaches of the firm’s independence policies and procedures to determine whether they create a threat to independence for the audit engagement.
                    <br><br>

                    I have taken appropriate action to eliminate such threats or reduce them to an acceptable level by applying safeguards.
                    <br><br>

                    Where applicable, I have promptly reported to the CEO and the OMQC, any failure to resolve such matters so that appropriate action can be taken.
                    <br><br>

                    I have documented conclusions on independence and any relevant discussions with the firm that support these conclusions in the audit file.
                    <br><br>

                    

                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
             



              <button class="btn btn-info btn-long" type="submit">Sign and Submit</button>
              <button class="btn btn-secondary btn-long" type="reset">Reset All Fields</button>

            </div>
            
          </div>
          </form>

        </div>
        <!-- /.container-fluid -->

      </div>
      <!-- End of Main Content -->

      <!-- Footer -->
      <% include partials/footer.ejs %>
      <!-- End of Footer -->

    </div>
